### Update Password (correct old password)
PATCH {{hostname}}/profile/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "oldPassword": "newpassword123",
    "newPassword": "anothernewpassword123"
}

### Update Password - Wrong old password (should fail with 401)
PATCH {{hostname}}/profile/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "oldPassword": "wrongpassword",
    "newPassword": "shouldnotwork123"
}

### Update Profile - Empty fields (should fail with 400)
PATCH {{hostname}}/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "username": "",
    "name": ""
}

